//	Enable: Allows to activate or deactivate specified language, 0/1
//
//~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
//~~ List of languages should match list of available languages in ServerInfo.xml(bmd), LangInfo section
